{"tid":250617,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【殼王挪威墮海】阿叻：平日做得善事多避過一劫","createTime":"2017-05-20T08:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T08:54:00.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e990b67b6be20860bffd2db6b1c1fcc86db22c1","tid":250617,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:27:01.000Z","msg":"「殼王」陳國強早前在挪威坐直升機墮海，陳百祥（阿叻）今日出席《萬眾同心公益金》拜神儀式時說他本來也在直升機上，但因為想睇賽馬而決定延遲1日出發。他形容陳國強這次是九死一生，幸好當日乘坐的是新機，平日又做得善事多才能脫險。<br />\n<br />\n阿叻說︰「墮海後，英國機師被浮泡升返上水，他第2次潛入水中找不到陳生，第3次才救到他上來﹗陳生的律師朋友心臟停頓過3次，昏迷了5天才甦醒﹗幸好，陳生在水中能解開安全帶，他被救時清醒，但覺得海水很冷﹗」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170520/s00007/1495268312133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170520%2Fs00007%2F1495268312133&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=d826c45e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170520%2Fs00007%2F1495268312133&h=49841160\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170520/s00007/1495268312133</a>"},{"pid":"f79e94ba7e27f6ea17403953f370f78a58303fcd","tid":250617,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以係做得衰野多個天比教訓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c83276c6140456f2b3e56d78df6c87ea85059d6","tid":250617,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95777f0dabe90c29dfb34ae0e921861800d63f3e","tid":250617,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"串老細做得陰質野多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gi